        public void onDeleteCustomer()
                      throws java.sql.SQLException
        This method is activated once the "Delete Customer" button is clicked. Displays a message if no customer is selected. Displays a message if the selected customer has related appointments. Confirms that the user wants to delete the customer and deletes the record if the user clicks "OK". Refreshes the tables.
